<Title>Forward and Aft Cargo Handling System Control Panel Access Door</Title>
<DispatchCondition>
<DispatchConditionRemarks>
<Para>Any number may be missing provided electrical connectors to control panel are disconnected, capped and stowed.</Para>
<Note>
<Para>If a Cargo Handling System (CHS) Control Panel Access Door is removed, the hinge screws must be re-installed to prevent a pressure leak.</Para>
</Note>
<Note>
<Para>Disconnection between electrical connectors and control panels can cause the CHS to be inoperative. Airplane must be dispatched using MEL item 50-20-01.</Para>
</Note>
